<subSubSection id="75C19BACFFBB790DFF6C27B3606C8F6C" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="3D64C827FFBB790DFF6C27B3606C8F6C" blockId="10.[151,1436,718,923]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis id="0FAF1435FFBB790DFF6C27B363678F49" bold="true" box="[199,352,754,779]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Distribution.</emphasis>
Mainly in Pacific Isls, e.g. Solomon Isl., 
<collectingRegion id="FF1F06C5FFBB790DFC9327B261C18F49" box="[824,966,754,779]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="West New Britain" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">New Britain</collectingRegion>
